WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.929 --> 00:00:05.879
Welcome to twominenglish.com. Teaching you English through two-minute lessons.

00:00:07.006 --> 00:00:12.239
In this lesson you will learn how to 
 book a hotel by calling in advance.

00:00:17.960 --> 00:00:20.357
Hello, is this the Parkland Residency?

00:00:21.674 --> 00:00:24.329
Yes, I am Hans. How may I help you?

00:00:25.603 --> 00:00:26.852
I'd like to book a room for tomorrow.

00:00:28.004 --> 00:00:29.500
For how many people?

00:00:30.635 --> 00:00:31.628
Just me.

00:00:32.553 --> 00:00:35.513
Okay Sir. What's your complete name, please?

00:00:36.346 --> 00:00:38.985
Rouf Hughes. What is the total cost?

00:00:40.429 --> 00:00:43.236
That would be $120 per night.

00:00:44.623 --> 00:00:46.972
No problem. Book the room for one night, please.

00:00:48.226 --> 00:00:50.951
Sure, may I know your cell phone number?

00:00:52.405 --> 00:00:55.311
Yes, it's 345 344.

00:00:56.837 --> 00:00:59.112
Thank you. How would you like to pay?

00:01:00.442 --> 00:01:01.706
I can pay through credit card.

00:01:02.874 --> 00:01:07.214
Okay. I will call you back in about 10 minutes to confirm your booking.

00:01:08.464 --> 00:01:09.263
Thank you very much.

00:01:16.261 --> 00:01:18.825
Parkland Residency, this is Rouf. How may I help you?

00:01:20.197 --> 00:01:25.502
Hi, I'm Windy Dakota. I was wondering if I can get 
 a good suite for the 12th of this month?

00:01:26.665 --> 00:01:29.703
Sorry Miss Dakota, we have no vacant suites for that day

00:01:31.146 --> 00:01:33.487
Alright, then what about the 24th?

00:01:35.305 --> 00:01:36.266
Please give me a moment. 

00:01:37.468 --> 00:01:38.387
Sure.

00:01:39.893 --> 00:01:43.860
Yes, suites are available for that day, would 
 you like to book one for you.

00:01:44.939 --> 00:01:46.990
I'll have to call you back, thank you.

00:01:48.342 --> 00:01:49.050
No problem.

00:01:55.730 --> 00:02:00.210
Hello, this is Hans Schefield. What are your rates per day for a room?

00:02:01.728 --> 00:02:05.930
Mr. Schefield, we have rooms ranging from $100 to $500 per day.

00:02:07.537 --> 00:02:11.100
What's the price for family suite with 2 beds?

00:02:12.614 --> 00:02:19.140
Deluxe family suites start from $450. May I know for 
 how many people you would need the suite?

00:02:21.091 --> 00:02:23.370
We are four. Two adults and two kids.

00:02:24.577 --> 00:02:28.140
Great. It would be $500 for the best suite.

00:02:29.645 --> 00:02:34.850
Ah! That's expensive. Let me know if there's a good room facing the sea.

00:02:36.378 --> 00:02:41.740
One second... Yes, we have a fine sea-view suite for you. It is $350.

00:02:43.045 --> 00:02:44.540
Now that sounds nice!

00:02:45.818 --> 00:02:47.820
Will you be booking it, Mr. Schefield?

00:02:49.060 --> 00:02:50.150
Yes, please.

00:02:56.242 --> 00:02:58.980
Front desk, Hotel La Belle. How may help you?

00:03:00.215 --> 00:03:02.900
Yes, I called you an hour earlier. I'm Windy Dakota.

00:03:04.059 --> 00:03:06.860
Yes, Miss Dakota. Would you like to book a room now?

00:03:08.226 --> 00:03:11.180
Yes. But what are my payment options?

00:03:12.450 --> 00:03:18.780
We accept all types of credit cards. There is also 
 a special rebate of 5% on American Express cards.

00:03:20.733 --> 00:03:25.180
That's fine, but the problem is I don't have a 
 card! I only have a Visa checking account.

00:03:26.732 --> 00:03:27.730
Okay...No problem.

00:03:29.414 --> 00:03:30.380
Can I use my checking account?

00:03:31.882 --> 00:03:35.820
Yes, certainly.  You can use the debit card connected to your checking account.

00:03:37.417 --> 00:03:38.320
Thank you!

00:03:39.367 --> 00:03:41.530
You are welcome, Miss Dakota.

00:03:47.083 --> 00:03:48.220
I'd like to book a room for tomorrow.

00:03:53.493 --> 00:03:54.180
What is the total cost?

00:03:59.698 --> 00:04:00.820
Book the room for one night, please.

00:04:06.157 --> 00:04:09.250
I was wondering if I can get a good 
 suite for the 12th of this month?

00:04:19.054 --> 00:04:20.680
What are your rates per day for a room?

00:04:27.850 --> 00:04:30.020
Let me know if there's a good room facing the sea.

00:04:37.908 --> 00:04:39.480
But what are my payment options?

